## 🤖 Company RAG Knowledge Base Chatbot

This is a **smart Telegram chatbot** that answers questions about your company by reading your own documents — like having an AI employee who has read every file in your Google Drive and can answer questions about them instantly.

---

## 🗂️ The Big Picture — 3 Separate Parts

```
PART 1: 📁 New file added to Drive    → learns it
PART 2: ✏️ File updated in Drive      → relearns it  
PART 3: 💬 Someone asks on Telegram   → answers it
```

---

## 📁 PART 1 — Teaching the Bot (New File)

```
New file added to Google Drive folder
        ↓
Save the file ID
        ↓
Download the file
        ↓
Extract all text from it
        ↓
Convert text → AI embeddings (OpenAI)
        ↓
Store in Supabase vector database ✅
```

Think of this like the bot **reading and memorizing** a new document the moment it's uploaded.

---

## ✏️ PART 2 — Updating What the Bot Knows (File Updated)

```
Existing file is edited in Google Drive
        ↓
Delete OLD version from Supabase database
        ↓
Download the NEW version
        ↓
Extract text → Convert to embeddings
        ↓
Store fresh version in Supabase ✅
```

This keeps the bot's knowledge **always up to date**. If you change a policy doc, the bot forgets the old version and learns the new one.

---

## 💬 PART 3 — Answering Questions on Telegram

```
User sends message on Telegram
        ↓
    Voice or Text?
    ┌── 🎤 Voice ──→ Download audio → Transcribe with Whisper → Text
    └── ⌨️ Text  ──→ Use directly
        ↓
RAG Agent searches Supabase for relevant docs
        ↓
GPT-4o reads the matching docs + writes answer
        ↓
📤 Send answer back on Telegram
```

---

## 🧠 Key Technologies Explained Simply

| Technology | What it does | Simple analogy |
|---|---|---|
| **Supabase** | Stores document chunks | Filing cabinet |
| **OpenAI Embeddings** | Converts text to searchable math | Index at the back of a book |
| **RAG Agent** | Finds relevant docs + answers | Librarian who finds the right page |
| **GPT-4o** | Writes the final answer | The expert who reads the page and explains it |
| **Whisper** | Converts voice to text | Stenographer |
| **Window Buffer Memory** | Remembers conversation history | Short-term memory per user |

---

## 💡 Real Example of How It Works

> You upload your company's **FAQ, pricing doc, and refund policy** to Google Drive.
>
> A customer messages your Telegram bot:
> *"What's your refund policy for annual plans?"*
>
> The bot searches Supabase → finds the refund policy chunk → GPT-4o reads it → replies with the exact answer. No human needed. ✅

---

## ⚙️ What You Need to Use This

- Telegram bot token
- Google Drive folder (named `Marketing Ladder Knowledge Base`)
- Supabase account with `pgvector` enabled
- OpenAI API key (for GPT-4o, Whisper, and embeddings)

